articles.author: Michael Holden
articles.title: Prince Harry challenges 'unfair treatment' over UK security in London court - Reuters UK
articles.description: Prince Harry has been subjected to unlawful, unfair and unjustifiable treatment by the British government over the decision to take away his police protection when he is in Britain, his lawyer told London's High Court on Tuesday.
